        "content": "<p>ah yes, so... my approach to solving this would be to search the compiler for where the main diagnostic is emitted and then add a call to <code>note</code> on the diagnostic. This note should then explain what the current limit is and show an example of a use of the limit attribute with 2x the current limit</p>",
        "id": 277144637,
